{"tid":1378891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家，今次真係一齊響應罷工啦，好嗎？","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:56:10.000Z","uid":108120,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8221f9b78803c5d0f0b722224fc9197ec61e6fe","tid":1378891,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"我知大家都有自己既包袱，好多顧慮唔敢罷工，但當大家都一齊響應，個壓力就唔係你地自己身上，而係喺政府到。試諗下大量市民，尤其是公務員同埋交通工具前線員工，一齊不合作，唔返工會對香港經濟幾大威脅？<br />\n平時唔敢去發夢既各位，其實你地都擁有呢樣好強既武器係手，就係唔撚返工，求下你地今次真係一齊罷工啦，唔好再得個講字啦好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76eaead040c0a61061fa5a23a7a9c7578af178e","tid":1378891,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"f6079947f6a92fe2a241f0e269409f0dd33a9ef0","tid":1378891,"uid":108120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"香港前途一定緊要過返工"},{"pid":"3a801097d7523153ebb7265af86d140e2a7a8c0b","tid":1378891,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"因為我愛香港呢個家，所以我更加唔會幫出賣自己家園既政府貢獻"},{"pid":"3cf6b15cd21617c1ad9b76eb6c8ba286f6698f3b","tid":1378891,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d224764c143b071db84cb448afe2736c015eb2c","tid":1378891,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd15d5413e5c19599e908e6644d5b2ed2466107","tid":1378891,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a182fb7d50da139419e86a3428d53c5aed5c00","tid":1378891,"uid":248225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"如果聽日佢哋開會話出咩解放軍，停水停電，停工，大家唔洗理，當佢鳩UP。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我最怕聽日係政府放軟小小態度，例如話林鄭辭職，又撤回法例甚至話畀普選等等。 <br />\n<br />\n我預計會有以下情況出現：<br />\n1. 有一班打手上水話要接受政府退步，運動要停止啦。 <br />\n<br />\n2.或者飯民又接受政府開出既條件。<br />\n<br />\n3.又或者社會媒體又吹和談風。<br />\n<br />\n由此至終，五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係第五點，我地唔要中共開出既普選，要有美國監督下既普選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以今晚同聽日下午三點，文宣宣傳重申五大訴求，缺一不可。同時煲大今晚黑警罪行。<br />\n<br />\n咁辛苦走到呢步，唔可以因為政府小小甜頭而散。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特此預告！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378852/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378852/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"590ee58cdfbbe36be527542911493807d3f375b9","tid":1378891,"uid":194403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"罷"},{"pid":"9fd5547de839e7930dde9197014a67b270603681","tid":1378891,"uid":150625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19kbwZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19kbwZ8.png&h=6aaf04fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMcxgrO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMcxgrO.png&h=6e784ead&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcFbwZ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcFbwZ9.png&h=373ad213&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRi09MR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRi09MR.png&h=2849e28a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSPr5kb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSPr5kb.png&h=cf75d06c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoYAedw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoYAedw.png&h=304dd10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpj7H2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqpj7H2.gif&h=de954cf5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oB5zb9J.gif\